Title: NEWS FROM WASHINGTON.
Abstract: Private letters from Hilton Head lay the whole blame of the recent disaster in Florida upon Gen. SEYMOUR, who disobeyed orders in advancing beyond a certain point, which he was ordered by Gen. GILLMORE to hold, and to await the attack of the enemy. Our losses are stated to be larger than at first supposed.
